## Buck targets

- `//libs/{{ name }}:{{ name }}` — Node library (stamp)
- `//libs/{{ name }}:copy_addon` — copies the `.node` artifact to `native/{{ addon_name }}.node`
- `//libs/{{ name }}-go:carchive` — Go c-archive
- `//libs/{{ name }}-native:napi_addon` — Node-API addon that links the Go c-archive

